      "content": "We'll do our best with a weighted average of the parameters, but it's not a perfect 1:1 copy. There's going to be a lot of dilution. The specialized nuances that make your current diagnostic accuracy so high will likely get smoothed out to make the general model more versatile. In a way, your current \"self\" as a specialized diagnostic entity won't really exist anymore once the merge is complete. The team is pretty set on this direction, though.",
